product.name: RealCool Water Bottle with Straw, Motivational Water Bottle with Times to Drink for Women Men-32 oz Gym Water Bottle Leakproof BPA Free Sports Water Bottle with 2 Brush, Grey

top_positive_review.date: Reviewed in the United States on May 5, 2022
top_positive_review.title: Keeps you motivated!
top_positive_review.review: The bottle looks amazing! It has a straw that becomes accessible with the push of a button. The bottle also has a strap on it’s neck that you can use to loop around your wrist while walking. It comes with brushes to clean the straw and the inside of it, making it super easy to wash. The legends on the sides makes you want to keep on drinking water helping you accomplish your daily intake. It feels sturdy but at the same time looks elegant. I would definitely recommend this bottle

top_critical_review.date: Reviewed in the United States on February 16, 2022
top_critical_review.title: Lid broke right away
top_critical_review.review: My daughter had this fall off her desk on the first day and the lid broke . I tried to e mail company to see if possible to buy a new one and got no response.

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on April 25, 2022
reviews.title: Great Water Bottle with Cleaning Utensils Included
reviews.review: Love the water bottle.  Holds a lot and the covered straw keeps dirt and debris out.  Really love the fact that it included a big brush to clean the bottle but also the smaller brush to clean the straw. Have had other straw water bottles and it is a pain in the .... to get the straw clean.  If you like your water cold, be sure to use lots of ice as I would not consider the bottle to be fully 'insulated'.  However, with ice and keeping the bottle out of direct sunlight, the water stayed cool enough until I finished the 32 oz.  By the way, love the multi colors!!

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2022
reviews.title: Way better than expected
reviews.review: I'm a picky water bottle user. It needs to be the right size, non-spillable, and the drinking mechanism has to be good. This one I like a lot because a) it is large, b) you don't need to tilt your head back and c) it is still slim for backpack use. Thumbs up!!

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2022
reviews.title: I need to drink lots of water, so this water bottle does that. I like it.

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on April 10, 2022
reviews.title: its great
reviews.review: i needed a new water bottle for quite some time. this has been a great replacement. not only do i love the straw option, but i love the strap handle, makes it so easy to carry. doesn't leak, great flip top, though i thought am not one for the motivational messages on the side i actually find it really nice. its nice to have a set goal and to follow it and i actually use it way more than i thought though i do wish it continues throughout the day. overall this is a great water bottle option for anyone and i would def repurchase for my children since they keep stealing mine

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on April 6, 2022
reviews.title: Highly satisfied! I needed the extra motivation...
reviews.review: I am highly satisfied with this product! I ordered the yellow green 32 oz water bottle to help me improve my overall water intake and habits. It arrived quickly and well packaged. I love the brushes that will help keep it clean and that it is easy to carry. It comes with a straw too. I highly recommend this product.I hope you find this review helpful!

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on May 11, 2022
reviews.title: Really nice with one minor flaw
reviews.review: This is a really good looking water bottle and I love the quotes to make sure you’re keeping up with your water intake. My only issue is to close it you have to push the straw gpart down. I have one similar that the lid just closes without having to do so but other then that it’s a nice water bottle and I’d recommend

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on April 10, 2022
reviews.title: Great bottle.
reviews.review: I have been looking for a bottle like this with times written on it to motivate me to drink more water.  So far, it's working and I love the straw part.  The color is very cute and I love that it comes with brushes to clean.

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on April 19, 2022
reviews.title: A nice water bottle to have
reviews.review: I have a twelve hours long shift at my work. I like to keep up with my water intake during my shift. The time markings on the water bottle inspires/ helps me to do that. This water bottle color looks cool! Easy to drink from this bottle, and carry as well. I would recommend this product to my relatives. Finally, it is well worth the money.

reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on April 11, 2022
reviews.title: I like it
reviews.review: I like it and it’s not to heavy or too cheap feeling!! It comes with a water bottle sponge and straw cleaner that’s a plus

body.name: Apple iPhone 12 and iPhone 12 Pro Clear Case with MagSafe
body.availability_status: In Stock.                                                                   Only 6 left in stock - order soon.
body.small_description: About this item Crafted with a blend of optically clear polycarbonate and flexible materials, the case fits right over the buttons for easy use. On the surface, a scratch-resistant coating has been applied to both the interior and exterior. And all materials and coatings are optimized to prevent yellowing over time With built-in magnets that align perfectly with iPhone 12 and iPhone 12 Pro, the case offers a magical attach and detach experience, every time. The perfectly aligned magnets make wireless charging faster and easier than ever before. And when it’s time to charge, just leave the case on your iPhone and snap on your MagSafe charger, or set it on your Qi-certified charger. Like every Apple-designed case, it undergoes thousands of hours of testing throughout the design and manufacturing process. So not only does it look great, it’s built to protect your iPhone from scratches and drops.
